00:08:12.320 --> 00:08:14.130
ask me questions and
there was that sort

00:08:14.130 --> 00:08:16.760
of that direct engagement.

00:08:16.760 --> 00:08:23.560
And I guess one would
question how this course could

00:08:23.560 --> 00:08:27.620
be done electronically, or via
some kind of distance learning,

00:08:27.620 --> 00:08:29.120
or that kind of thing.

00:08:29.120 --> 00:08:33.620
Because that seemed
invaluable to me.

00:08:33.620 --> 00:08:36.090
That kind of personal contact.

