and without a Josh.

00:08:44.160 --> 00:08:46.660
GEORGE ZAIDAN: I mean, there
are versions of us in Missouri.

00:08:46.660 --> 00:08:48.250
ELIZABETH CHOE: There are.

00:08:48.250 --> 00:08:49.580
JOSHUA GUNN: I have an
