they're just fundamental facts,

00:09:04.340 --> 00:09:06.780
I guess, that you
should become aware of.

00:09:06.780 --> 00:09:11.200
But I gave a midpoint
survey to the students

00:09:11.200 --> 00:09:14.680
of what lectures have
you found most helpful,

00:09:14.680 --> 00:09:17.390
and they were all
like, all of them.

