00:10:51.190 --> 00:10:55.810
think you're going to
be an English major?

00:10:55.810 --> 00:10:59.110
CHRIS BOEBEL: And particularly
in media or video,

00:10:59.110 --> 00:11:02.940
it's like you have this
work, it's a piece of crap,

00:11:02.940 --> 00:11:06.110
