can be done to a script,

00:11:11.850 --> 00:11:16.040
to something that's been
shot and not edited the way

00:11:16.040 --> 00:11:17.715
it could be.

00:11:17.715 --> 00:11:20.120
It's a really
powerful experience.

00:11:20.120 --> 00:11:21.630
JOSHUA GUNN: Yeah definitely.

